creator: Mayur Pethani
descriptionHtml:
Expand your business with DailyPost
Daily Post Create a Post, Story, or Status for your Brand or Company, or Business We will add daily festival images in our app so all business or company can promote their business with the festival images on social media 365 days.
Do you want to expand your business? Now Download DailyPost App Just make your profile. Select a poster base on your business and make a business poster etc.

Download and share festival post images from custom frame, templates specially made to suit your business marketing needs with your Logo and Business Details on them. An opportunity for you to digitalize your business experience.
DailyPost Maker helps you to promote your business in this digital media.

You don't need a graphic designer to create a digital post for your business. We've designed a good collection of post templetes for many businesses and we made it editable so that you can customize them according to your needs.

DailyPost app will ease your job for creating & editing social media Post with ready-to-use poster design.

Take a look at the steps:

● Download the Application For Free
● Sign in with your contactno
● Add Your Business Details, Personal Profile.
● Add your Details (Name, Logo, Email, Address, Phone, etc.)
● Download Post and share in Social Media.

The Festival Images is entirely free to download, which means you can create as many Festival Poster as FREE.
YOUR RATINGS
Please leave us your ratings & reviews at Google Play.
